Greywolf Capital Management LP.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 10:42 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Greywolf Capital Management LP.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Greywolf Capital Management L.P. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets across the globe. It employs opportunistic credit-based and fundamental analysis-driven investment strategies. Greywolf Capital Management L.P. was founded in 2003, and is based in Purchase, New York with additional office in San Francisco, California.


4 Manhattanville RoadSuite 201Purchase, NY 10577-2119United StatesFounded in 2003



Phone: 914-251-8200

Fax: 914-251-8244

www.greywolfcapital.com







